INGREDIENTS FOR VEGAN CHEESE: 💛 margarine 💛 flour 💛 plant based milk 💛 nutritional yeast 💛 salt 💛 pepper 💛 spices 💛 turmeric . ♥️ How to make vegan cheese: melt 2 tablespoons of margarine in a saucepan and stir in 3 teaspoons of flour. Add 150 ml of plant based milk while stirring constantly. Stir in 4 tablespoons of nutritional yeast and season with salt and pepper.
